{
  "stem": "11175.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Every morning, I make it, straighten it out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I put the pillow down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The name-- it's-- I want to say the name, and it's hard for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But he-- so helped me a lot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the four weeks later, not even four weeks, but two, three weeks later, they liquidated that whole barrack.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That barrack, they liquidated completely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They took out the people, they shot-- they shot them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That's all right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "No more the Taunton barrack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "No people-- no more people bringing in, because the ghetto was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They didn't have people from where to bring them in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So this remained open, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "A open place.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I worked with them together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I worked in-- and I had that-- the soup what he's supposed to get every-- every day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, he gave an order that-- for who gave out the soup, then I should pick up the soup for him also.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had soup, and I have bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Everybody was around me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And these people-- you know, it's easy to say, the people, they were so hungry, if the farm sometimes a horse died, they took the horse and would cut it up.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they cooked it there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you found a piece of that meat in that soup, is wonderful.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, what I'm trying to bring out is, these people-- there were some people-- let's say, if you had that-- a bone found in the soup, and you were sitting and sucking out that bone and throw it away to the other guy, what he was so hungry, he picked it up, that bone, and he started to sucking it.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he threw it away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The third one comes over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the-- this-- this is the people that died first.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They died.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
